('Clinical-Grade Nutrition Counseling App', 'Health', 'Registered dietitian-supervised meal plans with AI food logging and lab integration. 42% of US adults are obese; medical nutrition therapy reimbursable by insurance since 2022.', '$5k–$30k MRR', '1M+/mo', '$6.2B', 78, 48, 87, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['nutrition','dietitian','obesity','telehealth']),
('Continuous Glucose Monitor Companion App', 'Health', 'AI coaching layer on top of CGM data for non-diabetics optimizing metabolic health. Levels raised $75M; Dexcom G7 available OTC; metabolic optimization market growing 120% YoY.', '$8k–$50k MRR', '400k+/mo', '$5.5B', 92, 45, 93, 'Explosive', false, ARRAY['fitness','CGM','metabolic','AI']),
('Hydration Tracking & Coaching App', 'Health', 'Smart water bottle integration with personalized hydration targets and reminders. 75% of Americans are chronically dehydrated; simple intervention with high engagement potential.', '$2k–$12k MRR', '2M+/mo', '$1.8B', 68, 55, 80, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['fitness','hydration','wellness','tracking']),
('AI Running Coach App', 'Health', 'Adaptive training plans with real-time form coaching via AirPods and smartwatch. 60M US runners; Garmin and Strava lack AI-personalized coaching; injury rate 50% annually.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '1.5M+/mo', '$3.2B', 74, 52, 84, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['fitness','running','AI','coaching']),

