('Hypertension Coaching App', 'Health', 'AI-guided lifestyle interventions with blood pressure tracking and cardiologist escalation. 122M US adults have hypertension; only 24% have it under control; $131B annual treatment cost.', '$5k–$30k MRR', '2M+/mo', '$7.5B', 78, 52, 87, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['chronic-disease','hypertension','cardiology','AI']),
('Asthma & Allergy Management Platform', 'Health', 'Inhaler adherence tracking, air quality alerts, and pulmonologist telehealth for asthma patients. 25M US asthma patients; $80B annual cost; 60% of cases preventable with better self-management.', '$5k–$30k MRR', '600k+/mo', '$5.5B', 76, 48, 86, 'Rising', false, ARRAY['chronic-disease','asthma','allergy','adherence']),
('Inflammatory Bowel Disease Tracker', 'Health', 'Symptom diary, food sensitivity tracking, and GI specialist telehealth for Crohn and UC patients. 3M US IBD patients with no dominant digital management app; flare prediction could prevent hospitalizations.', '$4k–$24k MRR', '300k+/mo', '$3.2B', 74, 40, 87, 'Rising', true, ARRAY['chronic-disease','IBD','Crohns','gut']),
