('Biological Age Testing Platform', 'Health', 'At-home epigenetic methylation tests to measure true biological age vs chronological age. Bryan Johnson Blueprint went viral; biological age testing market growing 200% YoY from near zero.', '$6k–$40k MRR', '200k+/mo', '$4.5B', 95, 38, 94, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['precision-health','longevity','epigenetics','biomarkers']),
('Personalized Preventive Health Platform', 'Health', 'Annual blood panel + AI risk stratification + personalized prevention plan. Function Health raised $153M at $1B valuation; $850 annual plan with 100+ biomarkers; market far from saturated.', '$12k–$80k MRR', '80k+/mo', '$8.0B', 84, 40, 92, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['precision-health','prevention','biomarkers','longevity']),
('Pharmacogenomics Drug Sensitivity App', 'Health', 'Genetic testing to predict which medications will work and which will cause side effects. 7% of US patients have preventable adverse drug reactions; pharmacogenomics 90% accurate predictor.', '$8k–$50k MRR', '50k+/mo', '$5.5B', 80, 38, 91, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['precision-health','pharmacogenomics','genetics','medication']),
