('Real-World Evidence Generation Platform', 'Health', 'Automates RWE study design and analysis from EHR and claims data for pharma companies. FDA increasingly requires RWE; pharma companies spend $2B+/yr on RWE studies manually.', '$25k–$180k MRR', '500+/mo', '$9.5B', 83, 32, 94, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['health-data','pharma','RWE','AI']),
