('AI Clinical Trial Matching', 'Health', 'Matches patients to eligible clinical trials from EHR data reducing enrollment time 80%. 85% of clinical trials fail to enroll on time costing pharma $600k/day in delays.', '$15k–$100k MRR', '1k+/mo', '$7.0B', 82, 34, 93, 'Explosive', true, ARRAY['health-data','clinical-trials','AI','pharma']),

